-- Centerra Gold Declares Inaugural C$0.06-Shr Dividend to Be Paid Sept. 8
-- JoAnne Norton
-- 2010-07-30T11:12:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/centerra-gold-declares-inaugural-c-0-06-shr-dividend-to-be-paid-sept-8.html

          
          
             Centerra Gold Inc., a mining company
with operations in Mongolia and Kyrgyzstan, said it will pay its
first dividend, 6 Canadian cents a share, to be paid Sept. 8 to
shareholders of record Aug. 18.  
          
          


  


        